msgstr ""
"如果只有一个可选的价格表，而联系人被指定了一个价格表，下拉菜单可能不会出现。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/price_management.rst:166
msgid ""
"If multiple selectable pricelists exist and match a visitor's country group, "
